Description: This guitar is from my personal collection. It is in like-new condition with no scratches, dents, or wear. Also included are a Fender guitar strap, cord, an extra set of guitar strings, and all the original paperwork including the manual. The Carved Maple Top Jazzmaster HH is a member of Fender's Select Series. Built in the USA this series one-ups the American Deluxe Series with choice tone woods, compound-radius fingerboards, beautifully figured tops, gorgeous finishes, and premium appointments throughout. This superb instrument is the ultimate production Fender. It plays like butter, and it sounds incredible. Fender Select Carved Maple Top Jazzmaster HH Features Include:· - Chambered alder body with flame maple top; hand-stained with gloss-lacquer topcoat· - Thick modern C-shape maple neck with hand-rubbed oil finish· - Channel-bound rosewood fingerboard, 9.5"-14" compound radius, with 21 medium-jumbo frets· - 25.5 scale length;1.685" nut width· - Two specially-voiced Wide Range humbucker pickups· - S-1 switch activates Frequency Mod, for fat single-coil sounds· - Deluxe staggered cast/sealed locking tuners· - Heavy knurled chrome Flat-Top knobs· - Adjusto-Matic bridge with stop tailpiece· - Fender Select Tweed case included
Title: FENDER SELECT CARVED MAPLE TOP JAZZMASTER HH
